OL,3,CWhat led to Gordon Gault falling
OL,4,Cvictim to knife crime?
OL,6,FOur Correspondent Kris Jepson explains
OL,7,Fwhat happened the night schoolboy
OL,8,FGordon Gault was stabbed
OL,10,FNewcastle schoolboy, Gordon Gault, was
OL,11,Fjust 14 years old when he was stabbed
OL,12,Fby Carlos Neto with a machete in the
OL,13,FElswick area of on 9 November 2022,
OL,14,Fbefore dying six days later in
OL,15,Fhospital.
