OL,3,CWhat led to Gordon Gault falling
OL,4,Cvictim to knife crime?
OL,6,FOn 8 March, 18-year-old Carlos Neto
OL,7,Fwas sentenced to nine years, two
OL,8,Fmonths, and friend Lawson Natty
OL,9,Fsentenced to 32 months in prison for
OL,10,Fthe manslaughter of schoolboy Gordon
OL,11,FGault.
OL,13,FNeto told the jury he had acted in
OL,14,Fself defence when using the machete.
OL,16,FDuring the trial, the jury heard how
OL,17,Fthe stabbing came amidst the backdrop
OL,18,Fof tit-for-tat violence between two
OL,19,Ffeuding gangs of teenagers.
