OL,3,CWhat led to Gordon Gault falling
OL,4,Cvictim to knife crime?
OL,6,FThe court heard Carlos Neto had
OL,7,Fallegedly been stabbed in the buttocks
OL,8,Fweeks before the incident and was
OL,9,Fseeking revenge. His "best friend",
OL,10,FLawson Natty, managed to buy two large
OL,11,Fmachetes online, according to the
OL,12,Fprosecution, which they both carried
OL,13,Finto Elswick Park on the night Gordon
OL,14,Fwas stabbed.
OL,16,FThe court heard the boys hid behind
OL,17,Fthe West End Women's and Girl's Centre
OL,18,Fnear the northern entrance of the
OL,19,Fpark, scouting out potential targets,
OL,20,Fjust after 6pm that evening.
