OL,3,CWhat led to Gordon Gault falling
OL,4,Cvictim to knife crime?
OL,6,FMeanwhile, back at Sovereign Place,
OL,7,Fnorth of the park, it appeared Gordon
OL,8,FGault and his friends had become aware
OL,9,Fthat the defendants were in the park.
OL,11,FCCTV played during the trial, showed
OL,12,FGordon Gault retrieving a metal
OL,13,Fbaseball bat from a bush and some blue
OL,14,Flatex gloves.
OL,16,FHe was then shown walking towards the
OL,17,Fnorth entrance of the park with his
OL,18,Ffriends, who were riding bikes.
