OL,3,CWhat led to Gordon Gault falling
OL,4,Cvictim to knife crime?
OL,6,FAs three of Gordon's friends rode
OL,7,Ftheir bikes through the park, CCTV at
OL,8,Fthe women's centre showed the
OL,9,Fdefendants watching them, before
OL,10,Fmoving towards the North East entrance
OL,11,Fof the park to lay in wait.
OL,13,FThe jury was shown CCTV, taken minutes
OL,14,Flater, showing Gordon and his friends
OL,15,Fgathering on Elswick Road, north of
OL,16,Fthe park, and then splitting up into
OL,17,Fthree smaller groups, each taking a
OL,18,Fdifferent route to the south end of
OL,19,Fthe park.
