OL,3,CWhat led to Gordon Gault falling
OL,4,Cvictim to knife crime?
OL,6,FGordon Gault was seen on CCTV riding
OL,7,Fpillion on the back of an e-bike, with
OL,8,Fhis friend, down Beech Grove Road
OL,9,Ftowards Westmorland Road, south of the
OL,10,Fpark.
OL,12,FThe jury was told the police believe
OL,13,FCarlos Neto caught Gordon Gault
OL,14,Funawares near a bus stop on
OL,15,FWestmorland Road.
OL,17,FThe jury was told he stabbed Gordon in
OL,18,Fhis arm with a machete, severing vital
OL,19,Fblood vessels and causing extensive
OL,20,Fbleeding. Neto told the jury he acted
OL,21,Fin self defence.
