OL,3,CWhat led to Gordon Gault falling
OL,4,Cvictim to knife crime?
OL,6,FAs Gordon was taken back to Sovereign
OL,7,FPlace on the bike, he left a trail of
OL,8,Fblood and dropped the baseball bat.
OL,10,FWhen he arrived in Sovereign Place,
OL,11,FCCTV showed him slumping off the bike
OL,12,Fand medics were then called to the
OL,13,Fscene.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, back in Brunel Terrace,
OL,16,Fjust off Westmorland Road, a fight
OL,17,Fensued between the remaining teenagers
OL,18,Farmed with machetes, knives and a
OL,19,Fmallet.
