OL,3,CWhat led to Gordon Gault falling
OL,4,Cvictim to knife crime?
OL,6,FThe jury was told another boy was
OL,7,Fslashed by Carlos Neto's machete, but
OL,8,Fhe survived.
OL,10,FAgain Neto told the jury he acted in
OL,11,Fself defence. The fight broke off when
OL,12,Fa witness drove her car between the
OL,13,Fyouths.
OL,15,FGordon Gault died in hospital on the
OL,16,F15 November 2022 with his mum by his
OL,17,Fside.
