OL,3,CWhat led to Gordon Gault falling
OL,4,Cvictim to knife crime?
OL,6,FWhen passing sentence, Mr Justice
OL,7,FMartin Spencer commented on the
OL,8,Fdangers and the prevalence of knife
OL,9,Fcrime.
OL,11,FHe said: "This is what is liable to
OL,12,Fhappen when young people arm
OL,13,Fthemselves with these kinds of
OL,14,Fweapons."
OL,16,F"Too many young lives have been lost
OL,17,Fas a result (of knife crime) and other
OL,18,Flives ruined in consequence. ..Too
OL,19,Fmany of these types of cases are
OL,20,Fappearing in court."
